7.	Write a query to identify the customer’s first name and last name based on their customer ID and brand (Emirates) from the ticket_details table.
ANS: Selected relevant customer info from customer and ticket_details table using a left join to combine the tables and using WHERE statement to limit returns only to “Emirates’. Used distinct here as list of customers was asked for and avoid duplicates.
CODE :

SELECT DISTINCT t.customer_id,
t.brand,
c.first_name,
c.last_name
FROM ticket_details AS t
LEFT JOIN customer AS c
on t.customer_id = c.customer_id
WHERE t.brand = 'Emirates'
ORDER BY t.customer_id ASC;
